PrecisAuthority to enter into AMENDING AGREEMENT NO. 3 with the nine participating Provinces (Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Nova Scotia, Ontario, P.E.I., Quebec and Saskatchewan) with respect to the NATIONAL TRIPARTITE PRICE STABILIZATION SCHEME FOR HOGS, providing for the termination of the scheme as of July 2, 1994.
